<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa-ah kipak in nuom un,
 Nanghaw lunggil diktak neite;
 Nanghaw, Amah deih a telte'n,
 Lungkham leh dahna nawhmang un.

[V2]
 Nuom un! Nuom un!
 Lalpa-ah kipakin nuom un!
 Nuom un! Nuom un!
 Lalpa-ah kipakin, nuom un!

[V3]
 2. Kipak un, Lal A hih ziekin,
 Lei leh vana lal lopi pen;
 A thu'n thil bawlin, vai a hawm,
 Tandawk dinga &quot;Mak&quot; leh &quot;Hat&quot; chuh.

[V4]
 3. Thudik panpih galdona ah,
 Na galten, hun zo vang mahleu;
 Muhloh Pathien sepaihte chuh,
 Nang hun dote sang a tamzawu.

[V5]
 4. Sunin thimna'n hun lieh mahleh,
 Zanin na chung van nim mahleh;
 Bangman hun hih lauthawng ki hen,
 Lauhum beih man ging det zingin.

[V6]
 5. Lalpa-ah kipakin nuom un,
 A pahchakna chu lan phuong un;
 Aw leh kingkang leh gihawih in,
 'Hallelujah' ti'n la'n sauin.</lyrics>
<title>REJOICE IN THE LORD</title>
<hymn_number>334</hymn_number>
</song>